<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="poemXX">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>eḵkuḷaṅ kaḻiya virunila maruṅki</l>
<l>ṉaruṅkaṭa ṉiṟutta peruñce yāḷaṉai</l>
<l>yāṇṭuḷa ṉōveṉa viṉavuti yāyiṉ</l>
<l>varupaṭait tāṅkiya kiḷartā rakala</l>
<l>maruṅkaṭa ṉiṟumār vayava reṟiya</l>
<l>vuṭampun tōṉṟā vuyirkkeṭ ṭaṉṟē</l>
<l>malaiyunar maṭaṅki māṟetirk kaḻiya</l>
<l>valakaip pōki citaintuvē ṟākiya</l>
<l>palakai yallatu kaḷattoḻi yātē</l>
<l>cēṇviḷaṅku nallicai niṟīi</l>
<l>nānaviṟ pulavar vāyu ḷāṉē.</l>
</lg>
